Bain Capital By the Numbers




1984
BAIN CAPITAL FOUNDED
From our founding as a private equity firm, we’ve extended our approach across asset classes to include public equity, credit and venture capital. And, we leverage our shared platform to capture cross-asset class opportunities in strategic areas of focus.




14
OFFICES WORLDWIDE
Our offices span four continents with locations in Boston, Chicago, Dublin, Hong Kong, London, Melbourne, Mumbai, Munich, New York, Palo Alto, San Francisco, Shanghai, Sydney and Tokyo.




900+
TEAM MEMBERS
Our people are the core of our competitive advantage—the greatest outcomes come from great teams.



 























































