Bain Capital Closes 3rd Asia-Focused Fund With $3B Raised



        By Benjamin Horney



					Law360, New York (December 15, 2015,  5:14 PM EST) -- Private equity firm Bain Capital LLC has closed a third Asia-focused fund after having raised $3 billion, a person familiar with the matter confirmed on Tuesday, with investments from the fund slated to begin once the calendar turns to 2016.The Bain Capital Partners Asia III LP fund will direct money toward investments throughout Asia, the person told Law360, though the firm has not disclosed anything publicly, and Bain team members themselves will commit “at least” $250 million in addition to the $3 billion figure....
				
